title: Easy Louisiana Pork & Creamy Slaw with Sesame Carrot Fries & Garlic Aioli
description: Give pork loin a dash of flair with a smokey Louisiana spice blend for a melody of robust flavours. Then, don’t stop there. Ramp up your dish with a creamy aioli slaw tossed around with cucumber.

